><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sfu-student-portal\/#What_to_Know_About_SFU_Student_Portal\" title=\"What to Know About SFU Student Portal\">What to Know About SFU Student Portal<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sfu-student-portal\/#Simon_Fraser_Student_Portal\" title=\"Simon Fraser Student Portal\">Simon Fraser Student Portal<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/sfu-student-portal\/#Simon_Fraser_Student_Portal_Check_Now\" title=\"Simon Fraser Student Portal | Check Now\">Simon Fraser Student Portal | Check Now<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>To view the <strong>Simon Fraser Student Portal, visit&#8230;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfu.ca\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.sfu.ca<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>We at <a href=\"http:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">ScholarsWW<\/a> are pleased to inform you about how to login to the Official <strong>SFU <\/strong>Student Portal Login, <em>Sign up,\u00a0how to create a Student and Staff Account at the Greenside Design Center College of Design Homepage is clearly stated below<\/em><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"what-to-know-about-sfu-student-portal\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_to_Know_About_SFU_Student_Portal\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc85734675\"><\/a><strong>What to Know About SFU Student Portal<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Simon Fraser Student Portal<\/strong> allows formal and prospective students in the College to create an account or log in to perform certain academic actions at ease including Course Registration, Fees Payment, Exam Results, Admission Online Application, Track Application Status, Acceptance Fees Payment, Transcript, Timetable, Academic Calander, Extra Credit Hours, Deferment of Admission and so much more.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"simon-fraser-student-portal\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Simon_Fraser_Student_Portal\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc85734676\"><\/a><strong>Simon Fraser Student Portal<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Student Login portal of the University is accessible as follows;<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"simon-fraser-student-portal-check-now\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Simon_Fraser_Student_Portal_Check_Now\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc85734677\"><\/a><strong>Simon Fraser Student Portal | Check Now<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>To view the portal, you will need your University Student Login ID and Password respective.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Go to the SFU Login Page at <strong>\u2026.<a href=\"https:\/\/www.sfu.ca\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.sfu.ca<\/a><\/strong><\/li>\n<li>Log in with your Login ID and Password,<\/li>\n<li>Click on the Submit or Login button.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>You should be redirected to your official portal where you can access all the information you need.<\/p>\n<p>If you have any questions or corrections regarding this post, Please, kindly Drop a Comment below and we will respond to it ASAP.<\/p>\n<p><strong>I HOPE THIS POST WAS USEFUL, PLEASE DO NOT HESITATE TO SHARE IT WITH FRIENDS!<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"SFU Student Portal \u2013\u00a0 | How to login to Simon Fraser student portal, sign in\/up, retrieve, recover, change&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1121,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[448],"tags":[831],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4761"}],"collection":[{"href